desc:
Marketing Executive 2 positions in Bangkok , 2 positions in Phuket
 
Qualifications:

Thai Nationality Female Aged between 22-35 years.
Bachelor’s Degree in Marketing / Business Admin or related field.
At least 2 year working experience in marketing / Sales function
Good personality.
Good command of English communication.
Knowledge in Pc skill (Internet /MS Office)
Good coordination and problem solving skills
Good people skill neat, patient, well-organized, responsibility 
Able to work under pressure and overtime if needed.
Own and able to drive a car to visit customers and events as and when required

Job Description:

Listening to customer requirements and presenting appropriately to make a sale;
Maintaining and developing relationships with existing customers in person and via telephone calls and emails;
Cold calling to arrange meetings with potential customers to prospect for new business;
Responding to incoming email and phone enquiries
Acting as a contact between a company and its existing and potential markets;
Negotiating the terms of an agreement and closing deals;
Gathering market and customer information;
Representing the company at trade, wine events and wine dinner;
Negotiating on price, costs, delivery and specifications with customer;
Advising on forthcoming wine product developments and discussing special promotions;
Reviewing your own performance, aiming to meet or exceed targets;
Gaining a clear understanding of customers' businesses and requirements;
Making accurate, rapid cost calculations and providing customers with quotations;
Feeding future buying trends back to employers;
Attending team meetings and sharing experiences with colleagues.

Basic Salary : Depend on Experience 
If your attributes meet our requirements, you are invited to apply online or write-in with full resume stating qualifications, work experience, current and expected salaries together with relevant documents, contact phone number and 2 recent photographs (1 full body and 1 half body photo) to :
